    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The budget for high-end LLMs is already gone for this quarter. The template system is basically free by comparison. Honestly, it's hard to justify the expense when the new system handles the basic stuff just fine. What makes you think a hybrid model would be worth the extra cost?",
